<detail_text><![CDATA[<P>

The Bitrix Site Manager allows using the same template for several sites on different languages. This opportunity is realized by means of the message files mechanism:

</P>
<UL>

<LI>
in the template HTML prototype are defined areas intended for text displaying (for example, titles, ALT attributes, controls text etc.); </li>
<li>then in these areas should be placed special source code that calls language files containing necessary text messages on corresponding language. 
</LI></UL>



<P><A href="javascript:ShowImg('/images/integration_course/messages/messag3.png',631,449,'Использование языковых сообщений в публичном разделе сайта')"><IMG height=200 alt="Нажмите на рисунок, чтобы увеличить" hspace=0 src="cid:resources/res65/ILBIk.dfLYc.8SmF6.messag3_s.png" width=270 border=0></A>&nbsp;</P>


<P>
